{"tid":2147514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《傳真社》：林鄭月娥幼子「家有急事」由美國返港","createTime":"2020-08-09T09:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T12:01:41.000Z","uid":219379,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fb5c736d61e38704b60dd69f969f3bfa9b7a7963","tid":2147514,"uid":219379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:46:09.000Z","msg":"《傳真社》報道，正在美國修讀博士學位的行政長官林鄭月娥幼子林約希，因「家有急事」返回香港。<br />\n<br />\n《傳真社》派人到林約希位於波士頓的住所嘗試接觸他，並聯絡到他的業主。報道引述業主指，林約希的室友在上月25日表示，與他失去聯絡數天。業主其後致電林約希，但收到當地電訊商公告指，由於線路限制，未能撥出通話。<br />\n<br />\n報道又引述業主指，林約希的室友其後透過社交網站Facebook收到他聲稱「家有急事」回港，他在兩日後曾經電郵回覆業主，會續租單位至明年8月，但之後一直失聯，目前行蹤不明。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，特首辦在報道截稿前未回覆《傳真社》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%82%B3%E7%9C%9F%E7%A4%BE-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E5%B9%BC%E5%AD%90-%E5%AE%B6%E6%9C%89%E6%80%A5%E4%BA%8B-%E7%94%B1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%BF%94%E6%B8%AF-063605355.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%25A4%25BE-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E5%25B9%25BC%25E5%25AD%2590-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2580%25A5%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E7%2594%25B1%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25BF%2594%25E6%25B8%25AF-063605355.html&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=38b125a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%82%B3%E7%9C%9F%E7%A4%BE-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E5%B9%BC%E5%AD%90-%E5%AE%B6%E6%9C%89%E6%80%A5%E4%BA%8B-%E7%94%B1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%BF%94%E6%B8%AF-063605355.html</a>"},{"pid":"ae3498653b78534db0820047de8965da43046294","tid":2147514,"uid":158899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:48:41.000Z","msg":"母債子還"},{"pid":"2a0a161a127b9736d316ffa6837c67898650b82f","tid":2147514,"uid":276273,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:50:52.000Z","msg":"返香港打柒個老母，事關搞佢畢唔業"},{"pid":"62dc8d9f5e519f96c1d337d6d3e4a6562e44da28","tid":2147514,"uid"